    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh. The suspension retains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback expected of the M-chassis. Recent valve clearance adjustments and a cooling system overhaul ensure the high-compression power plant operates at peak thermal efficiency. An ideal candidate for the driver seeking an unfiltered, analog performance machine.",
