    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, showing only the lightest evidence of road use, while the body panels remain straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows very little wear, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All interior technology, including the navigation system, heated seats, and high-fidelity audio, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, having recently benefited from a comprehensive service that included a synthetic oil change, new air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and the suspension provides a smooth, composed ride without any rattles or knocks. I have kept a folder of all maintenance receipts to provide the next owner with peace of mind regarding its history.",
